    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dig for resources!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drill into the depths of the planet as a mining robot. Explore the underground and collect various resources. Discover the secrets that lie deep inside the planets. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore different planets!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every planet is unique. Size, bioms, resources and much more differ from planet to planet. These characteristics not only change the environment, but also the approach required to successfully mine the resources. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142940/extras/b8e3987eb8f798a12bae25afee72855d.poster.avif?t=1732608097\" width=618 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142940/extras/b8e3987eb8f798a12bae25afee72855d.webm?t=1732608097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142940/extras/b8e3987eb8f798a12bae25afee72855d.mp4?t=1732608097\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Master different threats!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decide which adventure you want to embark on.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142940/extras/6d7139f269c4d70c2b3120840aab56ee.poster.avif?t=1732608097\" width=618 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142940/extras/6d7139f269c4d70c2b3120840aab56ee.webm?t=1732608097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142940/extras/6d7139f269c4d70c2b3120840aab56ee.mp4?t=1732608097\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the solar system!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel through the solar system with your spaceship. Decide which planets you want to fly to. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142940/extras/226615f0069de1afa0bac07a93674d5e.poster.avif?t=1732608097\" width=618 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142940/extras/226615f0069de1afa0bac07a93674d5e.webm?t=1732608097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142940/extras/226615f0069de1afa0bac07a93674d5e.mp4?t=1732608097\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade your robot!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Anyone can mine ores on peaceful planets! But only the strongest robots can mine the treasures of the most dangerous worlds. So go ahead, get stronger armor, faster jetpacks and, above all, bigger drills!</p>",
